Python wrapper for the Campaign Monitor SOAP API, which provides access to all API Methods.

Campaign Monitor API: http://www.campaignmonitor.com/api/

Original code by Christopher Cote of Entropealabs.


To install via pip:

	pip install -e git+http://github.com/ozan/cm-py.git#egg=campaign_monitor
	
Usage:

	from campaign_monitor import User
	user = User(api_key=YOUR_API_KEY)
 	print user.GetClients()
